stack

Interface StackInterface<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of elements in the stack

    public interface StackInterface<T>
    A Stack represents a last-in-first-out (LIFO) stack of objects.
    Author:
    jddevaug, jcollard

    • Method Summary
